languages.text: {n}Бригадиры нашли подход к моторным вандалам, пообещав им снедь, воду и поставки необходимого. В самих аркологиях поползли недовольные шепотки — Вольный Торговец, кажется, награждает за ересь особой милостью!{/n}

{n}The foremen have established a mutual understanding with the Engine Vandals by promising them food, water, and other necessary supplies. This gave birth to disgruntled whispers flittering throughout the arcologies — the Rogue Trader rewards heresy with special privileges!{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}The brigadiers have found an approach to the Engine Vandals by promising them food, water and supply of other necessities — the approach that would curb the disobedient heretics with food and other necessary supplies. This gave birth to the disgruntled whispers flying around In the arcologies — The Rogue Trader seems to reward heresy with special privileges!{/n}

languages.text: {n}领班氏族与引擎破坏者达成了和解，承诺为他们提供食物、水与其他必要补给。这样的决定在巢都内引发了不满的窃窃私语，说行商浪人滥用特权，为异端分子谋利！{/n}

languages.text: {n}Los brigadistas han establecido un acuerdo mutuo con los Vándalos del Motor prometiéndoles comida, agua y otros suministros necesarios. Esto ha dado lugar a murmullos descontentos que revolotean por las arcologías: ¡{mf|el|la} Comerciante Independiente recompensa la herejía con privilegios especiales!{/n}

languages.text: {n}准将は、エンジン破壊者に食料、水、その他必要な物資を約束し、相互理解の関係を構築した。そのため、ローグトレーダーが特別な権限で異端者に報いていると、不満の声がアークロジーのあちこちで囁かれるようになった...{/n}

languages.text: {n}Les Brigadiers passent un accord avec les Vandales mécaniques en leur promettant de l'eau et de la nourriture, entre autres approvisionnements, et cela donne naissance à des mécontentements au sein des arcologies... Enfin quoi, {mf|le|la} libre-{mf|marchand|marchande} qui récompense l'hérésie par des privilèges spéciaux !{/n}

languages.text: {n}Die Brigadiere haben eine Übereinkunft mit den Maschinenvandalen getroffen, indem sie ihnen Lebensmittel, Wasser und andere dringend benötigte Dinge versprochen haben. Das führte zu verärgertem Getuschel in den Arkologien — {mf|der Freihändler|die Freihändlerin} belohnt Ketzerei durch besondere Privilegien!{/n}

Bu hadise, hoşnutsuz fısıltıların arkolojilerin dört bir yanında yankılanmasına yol açtı. Fısıltılarda Hür Tacir'in kâfirliği özel ayrıcalıklarla ödüllendirdiği dile getirildi!{/n}
